{"tid":785172,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實知魚之樂up乜9？","createTime":"2018-08-19T04:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T07:38:55.000Z","uid":92792,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1e54bd2ce52c55d73c9b1c81b0bd6c448929545b","tid":785172,"uid":92792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"莊子與惠子遊於濠梁之上。莊子曰：「鯈魚出遊從容，是魚之樂也。」惠子曰：「子非魚，安知魚之樂？」莊子曰：「子非我，安知我不知魚之樂？」惠子曰：「我非子，固不知子矣，子固非魚也，子之不知魚之樂，全矣。」莊子曰：「請循其本。子曰汝安知魚樂云者，既已知吾知之而問我，我知之濠上也。」<br />\n<br />\n其實就咁睇，莊子就好似個小學雞，人地問佢：「你係邊到/你點知魚係快樂」，佢就答人：「我係濠水上知道」。感覺上好似好歪理。我理解有冇錯？"},{"pid":"e92410a334bcd54f478c24a4f585d7b882cf0670","tid":785172,"uid":198866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c82df70db55d58c04e92aeb9a4c210c6c149cc0","tid":785172,"uid":65598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"根本兩個都係小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece4c456d39327889be09631877421a0bfb4a760","tid":785172,"uid":192491,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"但後世好多人都重復佢地兩個小學雞既對話喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4800f182c88ac2f8553fd66fc3133243287c8599","tid":785172,"uid":138967,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"再過多幾百年，小學雞嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n反彈<br />\n反彈無回頭<br />\n<br />\n都可以變中文課文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31854f2e95357e28d7c9f591559b7d9e3d77dded","tid":785172,"uid":92792,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:21:32